{"tid":117772,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"隻貓條尾中間凹左","createTime":"2017-02-12T13:24:15.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-16T13:48:38.000Z","uid":34154,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"0d2c746ef2ae1bbde25aac8c892331b90acebb8c","tid":117772,"uid":34154,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-12T13:24:15.000Z","msg":"我家貓兄妹 差唔多4歲 絕左育<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/5o2uqxj8\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2F5o2uqxj8&h=22332664&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n呢隻係呀妹，佢呢排都好行得走得食得痾得玩得打得<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/znosjc4l\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fznosjc4l&h=02b7dce6&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n但係最近唔知點解佢條尾係圖中箭咀指住個位凹左入去 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我摸落去又唔覺條尾d骨凹左，我掂佢佢又唔痛 （如果佢痛應該會叫或者唔比我掂佢）<br />\n但係又唔知咩事 好驚佢唔知係咪有病 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/u27ta6s0\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fu27ta6s0&h=c4645d6c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"771902ab1d5cfa5065e3b2748be3f443956504de","tid":117772,"uid":4326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-12T13:26:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 笑左"},{"pid":"7fa52d3f222a84ac7bf0440384e8d5dc534363d5","tid":117772,"uid":9185,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-12T13:26:21.000Z","msg":"動物遇到危險會斷尾求生"},{"pid":"bb3221cacaa49e64789f3a4208402b089aa4e4e9","tid":117772,"uid":11895,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-12T13:27:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>動物遇到危險會斷尾求生</blockquote><br />\n你遇到危險會唔會斷啫求生"},{"pid":"5c67a35bde92fd416f9f9937b0292fd3e6f9d869","tid":117772,"uid":34154,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"c